transcript:

Executive: Yes, good morning sir.
Customer: Oh, good morning.
Executive: Maine kaha sir jo issue tha aapka resolve ho gaya?
Customer: Haan ho gaya sir.
Executive: Concern close kar du main?
Customer: Ji ji.
Executive: Theek hai sir. Thank you so much.
Customer: Theek hai.
